-- Perki catalogue expansion — PROPOSED, do not run until Ollie approves.
-- Verified against official UK provider pages 2026-07-08. Mirror into Perks_Rows.xlsx after running.
-- Conventions: perk_id = provider-tier-title slug; perks assigned to the LOWEST tier that includes them
-- (hierarchical providers); variant providers get one row per variant.

begin;

